title: 12/09/20 HOUR 1- Andy Staples
itunes:title: 12/09/20 HOUR 1- Andy Staples
description:
Andy Staples tells Dan that the Michigan and Ohio St game was cancled because Michigan just has too many Covid19 players. Andy says that Ohio St could have played Michigan and lost and still would have made the Big10 Conference Championship game.
